::Aerotaur::
    He starts to run after him when he realizes he has more important things 
to do.  He spins around and rushes back to Trinity.  He picks her up and 
rushes her to the CR chamber in the ship.  "I just hope I'm not too late," he 
thinks to himself.  He turns around and sees Technosis.  "Thank you, but who 
are you?"  He glances at Zeni, he looks beaten up but he'll make it a while 
more.
